title: Canadians can vote online for favourite restaurant in enRoute magazine's poll
text:
Canadians can vote online for favourite restaurant in enRoute magazine's poll Sai Woo is a fabulous space featuring gigantic floating button lighting by Lukas Peet. 
TORONTO - Canadians can vote online for their favourite new restaurant from a list compiled by Air Canada's enRoute magazine . 
The selection of 32 contenders, from Galiano Island in British Columbia to an oyster house in St. John's, N.L., are examples of the country's diverse culinary identity.
